        <div class="eyebrow">WHY "KIND STRANGER"</div>
        <div class="prose">
            <p>The name is the methodology. You earn attention in a community by being the generous, helpful stranger who adds something — not the marketer who crashes the party to sell. Candor, usefulness, and respect for the room. It's also the anti-shill promise our clients are quietly buying.</p>
